{"tid":1707183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"雜物戰術","createTime":"2019-11-11T09:05:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T10:33:16.000Z","uid":32511,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"36401a6c30aab2abd8317e838892cedfd3f60534","tid":1707183,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:05:04.000Z","msg":"今日黎明行動係好成功，除左有手足中槍同被拉外。但可以改善如下：<br />\n<br />\nKeep住每日24小時做，每人10舊，100人一區，3分鐘內條街有1000舊雜物。扔完等9黎做路人甲乙丙，黑9走左再扔，目測每次黑9只有20-30人，Keep住做黑9必敗。"},{"pid":"d0dcbfc4a400d539291ce67680a13665522fb61c","tid":1707183,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/CmyrFgR.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"1239c8e2ca429cc05ab632bbc1c3690f10c4d393","tid":1707183,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8ae1372a5e068d20d62205b8939e3a6c50b50a","tid":1707183,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee406f37ff365c5c23f2aa65040b8cbe60536a98","tid":1707183,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:15:09.000Z","msg":"